{"TopicId":223750,"ForumId":130,"TopicTitle":"2.5x Scaled Missions [v0.3.1 for KSP2]","CreatedByName":"PhilippeDS","CreatedById":204559,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-18T19:06:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"PhilippeDS","CreatedById":204559,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-18T19:06:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003ESCALED MISSIONS\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003EUpdates the mission in Exploration Mode to match the 2.5x scale of Kerbolar System.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003ESpacedock:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3564/ScaledMissions\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/3564/ScaledMissions\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003EGithub:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/PhilouDS/ScaledMissions\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/PhilouDS/ScaledMissions\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003EAuthor: \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/204559-philippeds/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022204559\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/204559-philippeds/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@PhilippeDS\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0with the kind help of \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/226483-cheese3660/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022226483\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/226483-cheese3660/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@cheese3660\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKnown Issues:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EThe Keostationary Orbit mission is not validated even if the conditions are met.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\nLet me know if you find something wrong \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDependencies:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#333333;font-size:15.1181px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3536/2.5x%20Kerbolar%20System\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbolarUpscale \u003C/a\u003E\u0026gt;= 0.3.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3482/Patch%20Manager\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EPatchManager \u003C/a\u003E\u0026gt;= 0.5.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3277/Space%20Warp%20\u002B%20BepInEx\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceWarp \u003C/a\u003E\u0026gt;= 1.7.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-02-19T20:10:59Z\u0022 title=\u002202/19/2024 08:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Feb 19\u0022\u003EFebruary 19\u003C/time\u003E by PhilippeDS\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PhilippeDS","CreatedById":204559,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-19T14:49:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nv 0.3.1 is on spacedock. The Keostationary Orbit mission has been fixed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PTNLemay","CreatedById":30142,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-19T18:29:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo without this fix will the missions not work properly in the upscaled solar system?\u00A0 Is it something minor, like you need to reach a different altitudes.\u00A0 Or is it really game-breaking, like the target orbit appears under the planet/moon\u0027s surface?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PhilippeDS","CreatedById":204559,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-19T20:10:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe values was given in km instead of in meters so the mission wasn\u0027t validated even with a craft in a Keostationary orbit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cheese3660","CreatedById":226483,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-19T22:07:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224367372\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223750\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708367399\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002230142\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PTNLemay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, PTNLemay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr is it really game-breaking, like the target orbit appears under the planet/moon\u0027s surface?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome of the orbital ones would have a lot tighter requirements, and then stuff like the original Keostationary orbit would have incorrect orbital speeds and not be possible\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mitokandria","CreatedById":222458,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-16T21:23:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to make this 10x?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(i know the parts aren\u0027t exactly scaled to work with 10x...but still.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-03-16T21:23:34Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2024 09:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Mar 16\u0022\u003EMarch 16\u003C/time\u003E by Mitokandria\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PhilippeDS","CreatedById":204559,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-17T20:18:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is possible but not from the actual patch. All the values are hardcoded for 2.5x. So it\u0027s possible to do new patches for 10x. Do you use any particular mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mitokandria","CreatedById":222458,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-17T20:55:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA custom patch for Kerbol Upscaled (aka the 2.5x mod) to make it 10x, but there seems to be a few issues with the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E sinking into the ground at the moment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}